I"ª<h1 id="add-as-new-employee">Add as New Employee</h1>

<p>If you want to add a causal employee(person) or a trainee as an employee, you can use this option.</p>

<p>Right-click on trainee or casual employee(person) and select <strong>New Employee</strong>.</p>

<p>If this person is already an employee, it will show this message.</p>

